Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Pat Schroeder pitches in
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0440fjs
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Aug 1987
The woman who coined the 'Teflon President' nickname throws her hat into the Democrat ring. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less